      "description": "Task ID: AUDIT-PIXEL-UI\n\nObjective: Full UI/UX audit of Mission Control. Make it sales-ready and professional for customer demos.\n\nAudit Focus:\n1. Professional appearance: colors, typography, spacing\n2. Mobile responsiveness (test on small viewport)\n3. Dashboard clarity: can a manager understand board health in 10 seconds?\n4. Loading states, error states, empty states\n5. Navigation: intuitive and fast\n6. Cost dashboard: visually compelling for stakeholder presentations\n7. P10 Brain Health Drilldown: implement if not done\n\nDefinition of Done:\n- Written audit report: critical/medium/nice-to-have findings\n- UI fixes for critical issues (e.g., broken layouts, unreadable text)\n- Mobile test: viewport 375px pass\n- Professional polish recommendations\n\nReturn format:\n- EXECUTION_STATUS\n- RESULT_SUMMARY\n\nOwner: Pixel",
